reviews.review_text:
Prime 76 Dead Aside from a few duds in the first set, this is prime 1976 GD. 
The second set of this show, starting with “Lazy Lightning’”, rivals the awesomeness of the previous night, though both are musically very different.
Both the July and Fall shows of 1976 all have a different energy than the June shows, and you can start to hear it here.
